<Chapter Label="Chapter_`FGAb`">
<Heading><Code>FGAb</Code></Heading>

<P/>
The matrices and vectors used in our data structures are <Code>MatrixObj</Code> and <Code>VectorObj</Code>. The reason for using them is that we often encounter 0-dimensional matrices and vectors. However, you don't need to be worried about it as a user, since most functions support naive matrices and vectors.
<P/>
